[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10822] landed the initial implementation of a uutils version of 
``mv``
NotLebedev improved the 
``to xml``
 command by adding support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11577] self-closed tags
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11536] disabling automatic escaping
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11550] added a CLI flag to disable history
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11402] made sure that Nu does not block signals for child processes
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11576] fixed a bug in 
``uu_mv``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11436] adjusted some commands' input/output types
abusch fixed bugs in 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11567] the 
``items``
 command
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11504] ``commandline --cursor-end``
h7kanna 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11552] fixed up code coverage
flying-sheep 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11547] fixed a deprecation warning in default_config.nu
SUPERCILEX 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11532] improved shell integration to show the last command and running commands in the title
michel-slm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11572] replaced 
``htmlescape``
 with the better-maintained 
``v_htmlescape``
MarikaChlebowska 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11030] fixed the parsing of strings with special characters
DonSheddow 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11496] extended math commands to allow tables and records as input
drbrain 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10955] allowed plugins to receive configuration from Nushell configuration
atahabaki 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10872] added a 
``path exists``
 flag to skip traversing symlinks
dead10ck 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10232] improved the memory consumption of 
`
into sqlite
``
nibon7 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11508] applied nightly clippy fixes
